EN: This traditional handicraft is gradually falling behind modern technology.

ZH: 这个行业需要加强创新才不会落后。
EN: This industry needs to strengthen innovation in order to avoid falling behind.

ZH: 他们的观念太保守，导致整个团队都落后了。
EN: Their conservative ideas have caused the entire team to lag behind.

